│ comparisons (including constants) via the general bitwise transformation      │
│ section that follows. The generic lowering is correct and will yield          │
│ simplifications such as A ^ 0 -> A and ~(A ^ 1) -> ~A naturally via           │
│ subsequent instcombine rules.\nEdit details:\n  File:                         │
│ llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineCompares.cpp\n  Lines: 7175-7193\n │
